#. Tag: member
#: man-kmymoney.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The full documentation for &kmymoney; is maintained as a docbook manual. If "
"the &khelpcenter; program is properly installed at your site, the command "
"<userinput> <command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kmymoney</"
"parameter> </userinput> should give you access to the complete manual. "
"Alternatively the manual can be browsed in &konqueror; giving it the "
"<acronym>URL</acronym> <ulink url=\"help:/kmymoney\">help:/kmymoney</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"La documentación completa de &kmymoney; se mantiene como un manual docbook. "
"Si el programa &khelpcenter; está correctamente instalado en su sitio, la "
"orden <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/kmymoney</"
"parameter> </userinput> debería darle acceso al manual completo. "
"Alternativamente, se puede navegar por el manual desde &konqueror;, dándole "
"la <acronym>URL</acronym> <ulink url=\"help:/kmymoney\">help:/kmymoney</"
"ulink>."

